She found perfection in every detail and says, ‘I don’t think there ia anyone better than her in India!’ 💄✨

Aliya Baig brings over 12 years of experience and the expertise of working with 20,000+ brides into her teaching. She’s an educator who genuinely believes in sharing everything she knows—techniques, tips, and real-world insights—to help you grow as a makeup artist. No secrets, no shortcuts, just pure, honest guidance to take your craft to the next level.

Enrollments are now open for the FEB 2025 batch of the Masterprogram and will close soon. Take that empowering decision you’ve been waiting for and enroll now!

For more info, visit www.abam.in/academics or WhatsApp us at +91 8008740119.

IMA artists are the best in the world because they undergo rigorous, in-depth training focused on practical excellence. Certified only after passing stringent evaluations by independent London examiners—assessing every detail from technique to hygiene—they set the gold standard in artistry. 🌟🎨 #IMAExcellence #WorldClassArtists

ABAM is only the 3rd in Asia to be accredited with IMA. Registrations open for Feb 2025. Whatsapp us at +918008740119

Meet one of our brightest stars Malavika who traveled all the way from Trivandrum, stepping out of her hometown for the very first time, carrying dreams in her heart and courage in her soul. Despite the challenges and hardships, she chose to believe in herself and trust ABAM with her future.

Today, she stands as a proud graduate, having completed her course with flying colors. Her journey is an inspiration for anyone with a dream, proving that no obstacle is too big when you have the right guidance and determination.

We are so proud to have been a part of her transformation and honored to be called the best decision she ever made. If she can do it, so can you. Let ABAM be the bridge between you and your dreams.
